channel.title: VPS Problems - Help?
channel.description: EDIT : FIXED THE PROBLEM WOOT. Solution - I'm running a Windows 7 computer and it can be sketchy to run a 317-377-459-479 Server on my brand of PC. So in order to make my pc be able to compile and run.. I have to use Program files (x86) blah blah.. The VPS im using is a XP version of windows with 10gb and lots of ram, so i figured windows xp.. windows xp enviromental variable set up.. wrong... ALWAYS set up your enviromental variables when using a VPS according to your computer specs, not the vps! And whola, i'll probally make a tut on it later because I've googled it and everything.. and not alot of people know how to fix it so they end up spending 20$ for nothing. Thank you guys for your help, you may now lock this topic.
